File  Filtered  Mean   StdDev   Mean   StdDev  Confidence  Change
M2TS  No        861.7  8.2      650.5  8.1     100.0%      +32.5%
MKV   No        868.9  7.4      731.7  9.0     100.0%      +18.8%
